.right
  :&markdown
    We really want you to get involved in the #{project_name} and we love [contributions](contributing.html). One of the easiest ways to get involved is to join the community discussions.

    The main mailing list is hosted at the [fabric google group](http://groups.google.com/group/fusefabric).

     * [http://groups.google.com/group/fusefabric](http://groups.google.com/group/fusefabric)

    Please join us! 

    Be aware that to reduce spam your first post will be moderated through; so please be patient. (Unfortunately we get a lot of spam)

